Efence setup:
1) (as root)
echo 200000 > /proc/sys/vm/max_map_count

2)as user, run gdb, for example:
gdb ./berusky2/src/berusky2

3) copy and paste into gdb following :
set env DISPLAY=:0
set env LD_PRELOAD=libefence.so.0.0
set env EF_ALLOW_MALLOC_0=1
run

